com.netflix.governator.configuration

Interface ConfigurationProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractObjectConfigurationProvider, ArchaiusConfigurationProvider, CompositeConfigurationProvider, DefaultConfigurationProvider, LifecycleConfigurationProviders, PropertiesConfigurationProvider, SystemConfigurationProvider

    public interface ConfigurationProvider
    Abstraction for get configuration values to use for fields annotated with Configuration
